OpenOffice.org add-in

  Implementation of the {{{http://www.geoapi.org/geoapi-openoffice/index.html}GeoAPI add-in for OpenOffice.org}}
  using the Geotk library. This pure-java implementation supports all the formulas documented in the GeoAPI page,
  plus some additional ones. For example, the add-in provides coordinate transformation services as formulas inside
  the Calc spreadsheet.

